      "title": "Commander Vicum goes to the Army Hospital to see the wounded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Army Commander Lt. Gen. Vikum Liyanage visited the Army Hospital yesterday to see the well-being of the military personnel who were attacked and injured during the recent unrest at Polduwa Roundabout in Battaramulla.",
        "There, the army commander went to all the injured military personnel and inquired about their well-being."
